Name: The Classic KAS & IAS Study Circle
Details: Dharwad, regarded as cultural capital of Karnataka, is also well known for educational institutions. 18 years ago, the world was not as fast as today. Karnataka, particularly North-Karnataka, had no conducive atmosphere for competitive examinations as there was no awareness. Considering the hurdle, Mr Laxman S Uppar, an engineer by qualification, took the initiative of providing coaching for various competitive examinations. As a result, The Classic KAS & IAS Study Circle was started in February 1997 in Jayanagar of Dharwad.Started with a few aspirants of various services, now the Classic Study Circle is providing coaching for over a thousand candidates on regular basis. There are at least two to three batches, each batch of 100 students, preparing for exams like the IAS/IPS, KAS, PSI, Banking, teachers appointment, FDA, SDA, PDO, PC and others. So far as quality of teaching is concerned, the Classic Study Circle is unique in whole Karnataka as its faculty members are well trained and experienced in different subjects. The focused teaching, based on syllabus and previous questions of respective examinations, has been helping the candidates to gain knowledge required for the competitive examinations in shortest possible time

Details:
Edstar, set up in the year 2003 is a leading name in the field of Overseas Education. We operate through our network of 15 self-owned offices across India, and one in Kathmandu, Nepal. Each office is supported by well qualified professionals and education experts and works towards guiding Indian students in their admission requirements for overseas study.
Not only have we trained students in admission tests but have also helped over 2000 students set foot in a University of their choice across the world by means of our personalized coaching and counseling services through our locations across the country - major cities being Delhi, Bangalore, Mumbai, Kolkata, Pune etc. Backed by the expertise and strong industry connections of WLC College, our students have also found suitable placements with ease while still studying in foreign countries.
Be it Engineering, Medicine, Bio-technology, Law, Business Management, Fashion, Media, Art and Design or Hospitality to name a few, our end to end services have the best partners for studying in any destination overseas. Our major partners are spread mostly in UK, USA, New Zealand, Australia, Germany and Canada.
Thousands of satisfied and successful students bear testimony to the quality of our service and the missionary zeal of our consultants.
Not surprisingly, our students have landed in the most prestigious universities for the most sought after courses. This is further certified by the fact that the number of students availing our services is increasing with each passing day. Our reliability ensures flawless admission process and total satisfaction not only for the students but also for the partnering Universities

Details:
Teaching is a noble profession. It was the 'Teacher' in me and Gayathri (my wife), which brought us close to one another. Whilst we worked as teachers, in colleges and schools during the First decade of our married life, there was strong desire in us to build a teaching institute in Hubli (our home town) to cater the educational needs of Hubli. We started a modest coaching institute (FEAT Tutorials) in our home for students of Std. X. This was in 1999. In the year 2000 we were the first teachers in Hubli to make use multimedia teaching aids for teaching. We gained recognition as good teachers.
In the year 2004, BASE Bangalore, a leading coaching and training institute in Karnataka State, approached us to join hands to spread quality education in this part of the state. BASE is known as a premiere coaching and training institute in India. BASE has programs to train students to be achievers in the national level IIT-JEE, AIEEE, Medical Excel, and such other examinations. Students from Std. VIII to Std XII attend these programs in large numbers. FEAT Tutorials became a franchisee of BASE Bangalore.
